{{> _header title="Lists" navigation=global.navigation }}

<p>
	A list contains a single column of related options (based on the context around it) for the user to choose from.
	Lists can contain text, icons, or both and can expand to multiple lines if needed.
</p>
<p>
	In order to use Design System Lists, you need to import <code>/components/_lists.scss</code>
	partial in your SCSS file
</p>

<section>
	<h2 id="list">List</h2>
	<p>To display a regular list, add <code class="format-code">.wds-list</code> class in your <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> tag.</p>

	{{#component-demo}}
<ul class="wds-list">
  <li>List element 1</li>
  <li>List element 2</li>
  <li>List element 3</li>
</ul>
	{{/component-demo}}
</section>

<section>
	<h2 id="big-list">Big list</h2>
	<p>To display list with more space around its elements, add class <code class="format-code">.wds-has-big-items</code>. This modificator makes padding broader and font size bigger in each element. </p>

	{{#component-demo}}
<ul class="wds-has-big-items wds-list">
  <li>List element 1</li>
  <li>List element 2</li>
  <li>List element 3</li>
</ul>
	{{/component-demo}}
</section>

<section>
	<h2 id="list-with-separators">List with line separator</h2>
	<p><code class="format-code">.wds-has-lines-between</code> class adds subtle separator between each element of your list.</p>

	{{#component-demo}}
<ul class="wds-has-lines-between wds-list">
  <li>List element 1</li>
  <li>List element 2</li>
  <li>List element 3</li>
</ul>
	{{/component-demo}}
</section>

<section>
	<h2 id="list-linked">List with linked items</h2>
	<p>For lists with linked elements, like menus, use class <code class="format-code">.wds-is-linked</code> - it expands <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> node inside list elements to be fully clickable, without any gaps around. It is necessary to remember about adding anchor <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> wrapping each elements content.</p>

	{{#component-demo}}
<ul class="wds-is-linked wds-list">
  <li>
    <a href="http://wikia.com">Linked element 1</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="http://wikia.com">Linked element 2</a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="http://wikia.com">Linked element 3</a>
  </li>
</ul>
	{{/component-demo}}
</section>
